1.基本用法
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	.box1{width:30px;height:30px;background:#ddd;}
	.box1:hover{width:1000px;height:100px;background:#fcc;}
	.box1{transition:1s width,1s 3s height} /* 1s 10s[延迟] width,1s 5s[延迟] height */
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="box1"></div>
</body>
</html>
2.离开触发
  即 先进先出，后进后出原则。
